own 7 new "nexus-local: try-and-revert + orthogonality wrapper mandate (anima own 9 cross-repo mirror — raw 142 D2/D3 nexus scope)"
  slug nexus-try-revert-orthogonality-wrapper
  enforce advisory
  base raw 142 autonomous-loop-self-improvement-empirical-discoveries D2 + D3
  since 2026-04-28 (anima own 9 cross-repo mirror per raw 47)
  scope nexus tool/*.hexa pipeline-affecting algorithm dispatch + drill cycle / blowup detect / consensus loop transform sites
  rule nexus pipeline-affecting algorithm dispatch MUST apply try-and-revert wrapper + role-tag declaration:
  note D2 try-and-revert: every algorithm dispatch produces trial output, compares bytes, reverts if no improvement (`if len(trial) < pre { stage = trial }`)
  note D3 orthogonality: primary-attack roles (compete in best-of-N) vs secondary-stacking roles (always-fire post-winner) vs cross-file (A19 family) explicitly tagged via `@role(primary-attack | secondary-stacking | always-fire | cross-file)` annotation
  enforcement nexus/tool/*.hexa new algorithm dispatch sites MUST: (a) try-and-revert wrapper at transform-applying call site, (b) algorithm role-tag meta declaration, (c) raw 91 honest C3 — no wrapper = regression risk (Phase 8 P7 -2pp empirical evidence).
  exception design-stage exploration / pure measurement (no transform) artifacts exempt. ALL algorithm transform sites mandatory.
  bans algorithm dispatch without try-and-revert wrapper on transform-applying sites
  bans best-of-N expansion without orthogonality role-tag declaration (Phase 8 P7 falsified hypothesis re-occurrence guard)
  why raw 142 cross-repo validation D2+D3 FULL validate at nexus level — nexus drill cycle / consensus loop / atlas absorb pipeline have algorithm dispatch surface. Phase 8 P7 -2pp regression originated in hive but algorithm catalog is shared (A1-A19) — nexus applies same catalog → same regression risk class. Anima own 9 sister-mirror: nexus tool surface mirrors anima's, warranting same wrapper mandate.
  proof state/format_witness/2026-04-28_own789_cross_repo_mirror.jsonl (cross-repo trawl witness)
  proof anima own 9 entry 2026-04-28 + raw 142 cross-repo validation a71f4164
  proof nexus drill cycle / consensus loop / blowup detect = transform-applying dispatch surface (try-and-revert wrapper applicable)
  severity warn
